X1 = fft(wav01)

N1 = len(X1)
n1 = np.arange(N1)
t1 = N1/fs01
freq1 = n1/t1

plt.figure(figsize = (20, 6))
plt.plot(freq1, abs(X1))
plt.xlim(xmin=0,xmax=8000)
plt.xticks( np.arange(0,8000,250) )
plt.title('Homem - 22')
plt.xlabel('Frequency(Hz)')
plt.ylabel('Amplitude')

In [157]:
def plot_spec(Y, fs, title):
  plt.figure(figsize=(20, 10))
  ff, tt, sxx = scipy.signal.spectrogram(Y,fs,scaling='spectrum')
  sxx = np.log(sxx)
  plt.pcolormesh(tt, ff, abs(sxx), shading='gouraud')
  plt.title(title)
  plt.ylabel('Frequency [Hz]')
  plt.xlabel('Time [sec]')
  plt.show()
In [158]:
plot_spec(wav01,fs01,"Homem - 22")
In [159]:
plot_spec(wav02,fs02,'Mulher - 56')
